        <h3 class="card-title">Essential Broker Selection Criteria</h3>
        <p>Choosing the best spread betting broker is one of the biggest and most important tasks before you start to trade. Brokers play a key role in profit making.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Key points for your due diligence:</strong></p>
        <ul class="content-list">
          <li><strong>Regulation:</strong> Check whether the broker is regulated by financial authorities before anything else</li>
          <li><strong>Trading Platform:</strong> Ensure they offer reliable platforms like MT4, MT5, or proprietary solutions</li>
          <li><strong>Asset Range:</strong> Look for brokers offering a wide range of investment opportunities for diversification</li>
          <li><strong>Fee Structure:</strong> Understand all costs including spreads, commissions, and any hidden charges</li>
          <li><strong>Payment Methods:</strong> Check available deposit and withdrawal methods that suit your needs</li>
          <li><strong>Demo Account:</strong> Essential for testing the platform and strategies risk-free</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div class="insight-box">
          <p>‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Important:</strong> Fee structure is very important because several brokers impose hidden charges and commissions. Make sure the broker has a transparent and clear fee structure.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BEST BROKERS SECTION -->
