              </div>
            </div>
            <a href={broker.ctaLink} class="cta-button primary">{broker.ctaText}</a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RISKS SECTION -->
  <section class="section" id="risks">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">What Are Risks With Spread Betting?</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Understanding the risks involved before you start spread betting.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3 class="card-title">Important Risk Considerations</h3>
        <p>Like other forms of investment, there are a lot of risks associated with spread betting. Therefore, it's important to know about the risk factors before choosing a top spread betting broker and depositing real money.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Key risk factors include:</strong></p>
        <ul class="content-list">
          <li><strong>Leverage Risk:</strong> High leverage can amplify both profits and losses</li>
          <li><strong>Market Volatility:</strong> Rapid price movements can lead to significant losses</li>
          <li><strong>Account Close-out:</strong> Margin calls can force position closure at unfavorable prices</li>
          <li><strong>Market Gapping:</strong> Price gaps can bypass stop-loss orders</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div class="insight-box">
          <p>‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Important Note:</strong> Trading financial derivative products, in particular spread betting products, involve high amounts of risk. If you don't properly use stop losses, your initial investment is at risk.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Spread betting is not suitable for traders that cannot afford to lose large sums of money. Always start with a demo account and never risk more than you can afford to lose.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RISK WARNING -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="risk-warning">
        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Risk Warning:</strong> Spread betting carries a high level of risk and may not be suitable for all investors. You could lose substantially more than your initial investment. Past performance is not indicative of future results. Only trade with money you can afford to lose.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
  <section class="section section-alt" id="faqs">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-container">
        {faqs.map((faq, index) => (
          <div class="faq-item" id={`faq-${index}`}>
            <button class="faq-question" onclick={`toggleFaq(${index})`}>
              {faq.question}
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>{faq.answer}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      
